	<h2><a class="titles" href="./viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=16114&amp;sid=089fbd3ef9971294b9bfc4b0ba88e7a2">How do moving platforms work in your game?</a></h2>


	<p class="moderators">Moderator: <a href="./memberlist.php?mode=group&amp;g=320&amp;sid=089fbd3ef9971294b9bfc4b0ba88e7a2">Moderators</a></p>

